cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.IR 

The paper discusses the use of computer vision and deep learning methods for animal re-identification from camera trap data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the potential security and privacy concerns related to animal re-ID, which falls under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
